<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[Abstract This essay transforms a statement by writer Rubem Fonseca - that we live in a penal colony - into a guiding image to read his work. This text has three purposes: clarifying the spaces of confinement, the role of violence and the rarefaction of experience.]]></p></abstract>
